&gt; chooses it&#39;s bearer.  First Rodimus, now Leo Prime.  Let&#39;s go, we have a job
&gt; to finish.  ALL OF US!&quot;
&gt;
&gt; He roars back to Drill Bit with anger in his voice.

&lt;NEW&gt;

BIG CONVOY frowned mightily as he listened to DRILLBIT as well as
TUSCON, his optics going from one to the other. &quot;There is only one way
to resolve this.&quot; CONVOY said as he looked coolly at DRILLBIT.

&quot;If there is an answer it lies with Leo Prime and he is above us.&quot;
Turning to go up the tunnel began to march upward, MACH KICK and BREAK
following, the trip upwards far more difficult as the ground sloped up
sharply.

Ahead of them, echoing down the hall the voices, especially LEO PRIME
and the others could be dimly heard, they were perhaps several hundred
meters away, although in these tunnels sound seemed to travel farther.

Yes it was time to meet.

